title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 § 938.8 - Enforcement
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 § 938.8 - Enforcement

State Regulations
A late filing of a Client Semi-Annual Report, or failure to
file a Client Semi-Annual Report in accordance with these regulations, or the
filing of a Client Semi-Annual Report that contains false, misleading or
knowingly inaccurate statements are violations of either Legislative Law §
1-j or §1-o and subject a Client Filer to the fines and penalties
prescribed therein. Notes
